# LocalApache

This service allows you to create a local Apache service instance (on
OSX) so you can serve static content from your other services.

Should be useful to create an offline website.

Could be ported to Windows by including the Apache exe file.

Author: Dav Glass

Source Code: [http://github.com/davglass/bp-apache/tree/master](http://github.com/davglass/bp-apache/tree/master)
